data.description: Experience the epitome of comfort in this 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom haven with no HOA. Nestled on 1.61 acres, revel in the freedom of a fenced backyard, pool, and new decking ideal for privacy and outdoor gatherings. The walk-out finished basement offers versatility for your lifestyle needs. Perfectly situated near Richmond and Lexington, this home is a harmonious blend of spacious living, prime location, and modern comfort - an opportunity to relish the best of both worlds in a dreamy suburban escape. Plus, with an included home warranty, peace of mind is yours. Welcome to a lifestyle where every detail caters to your desires.
